      <div class="vision">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
          Our designs are inspired by the beauty of nature, encouraging a deeper appreciation for the outdoors.
          We’re more than just a brand; we’re a community. We support local initiatives and contribute to global causes
